title: Wi-Fi Connection Issues for Android 6.0 Marshmallow Upgraded Devices (University of Arkansas)
text: ( Source : University of Arkansas ) IT Services recommends mobile users do not upgrade their devices to the new Android 6.0 Marshmallow. Upgraded devices are currently unable to connect to secure campus Wi-Fi due to a compatibility issue. IT
